<HEADLINE>
<P>
2 PLEAS FOR PICKWICK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I have watched, with sadness, the lack of interest by Pickwick owners and 
managers in maintaining this world-known gathering place of some of the most 
famous names in skating. 
</P>
<P>
Instead of tearing it down, why not correct the problem? Bring in people who 
know how to make this training center profitable and are willing to work at it. 
</P>
<P>
Think about the hundreds of young people who will be deprived of their dreams. 
</P>
<P>
Must our figure skaters, hockey players, speed skaters, ice dancers, pair 
skaters, recreational skaters, show skaters, precision skaters and future 
Olympians be penalized? 
</P>
<P>
Is there anything more exciting than seeing "our kids" standing on the podium 
under that fantastic American flag at the Olympics? 
</P>
<P>
Please, don't close Pickwick! 
</P>
<P>
MARY KRAVETTE 
</P>
<P>
Costa Mesa 
</P>
</TEXT>
