ANGEL ATTENDANCE 
</P>
<P>
Sunday: 32,129 
</P>
<P>
1990 (49 dates): 1,580,444 
</P>
<P>
1989 (49 dates): 1,547,594 
</P>
<P>
Increase: 32,850 
</P>
<P>
1990 average: 32,254 
</P>
