<P>
James (Buddy) McGirt fought sluggishly with a sore left arm but boxed well 
enough to win a unanimous decision over previously unbeaten Jose Leonard 
Bermudez in a 10-round bout between two welterweight contenders in Atlantic 
City, N.J. 
</P>
