<P>
2 LIVE CREW CANCELS DATES; CAMPBELL IS 'EXHAUSTED' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A Wednesday concert at the Country Club in Reseda and another Friday at the 
Celebrity Theatre in Anaheim are among 11 dates canceled by 2 Live Crew due to 
the "complete exhaustion" of leader Luther Campbell. The controversial act's 
Los Angeles publicist said that Campbell's Miami physician has "ordered 
complete rest" for the performer. The local dates are are expected to be 
rescheduled for November. 
</P>
</TEXT>
