<TEXT>
<P>
Marlon Brando's son said he killed his half-sister's boyfriend in the actor's 
house during a struggle that began when the boyfriend "went nuts," a police 
officer testified today. 
</P>
<P>
Christian Brando said the fatal shot was fired accidentally as the two men 
wrestled over a handgun kept in the actor's Hollywood Hills mansion for family 
protection. 
</P>
<P>
